Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.81,0:26:03.45,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.28,0:26:10.22,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,鳴り止まない
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.14,0:26:18.80,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,spin-the-brand-new-lights!
